" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-menu w-5 h-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M4 5h16\"></path><path d=\"M4 12h16\"></path><path d=\"M4 19h16\"></path></svg></button></div></div></div></header><section class=\"relative min-h-screen pt-28 pb-0 flex flex-col justify-between overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none\" style=\"background-image:linear-gradient(to right, #1a1a1a12 1px, transparent 1px), linear-gradient(to bottom, #1a1a1a12 1px, transparent 1px);background-size:4rem 4rem;mask-image:radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 70% at 50% 50%, #000 50%, transparent 100%)\"></div><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10 w-full flex flex-col items-center text-center flex-1 justify-center pb-20\"><div class=\"mb-8 flex items-center gap-2 border-2 border-foreground px-5 py-2 bg-background brutalist-shadow\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-sparkles w-3.5 h-3.5 text-primary\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M11.017 2.814a1 1 0 0 1 1.966 0l1.051 5.558a2 2 0 0 0 1.594 1.594l5.558 1.051a1 1 0 0 1 0 1.966l-5.558 1.051a2 2 0 0 0-1.594 1.594l-1.051 5.558a1 1 0 0 1-1.966 0l-1.051-5.558a2 2 0 0 0-1.594-1.594l-5.558-1.051a1 1 0 0 1 0-1.966l5.558-1.051a2 2 0 0 0 1.594-1.594z\"></path><path d=\"M20 2v4\"></path><path d=\"M22 4h-4\"></path><circle cx=\"4\" cy=\"20\" r=\"2\"></circle></svg><span class=\"font-mono text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest\">Meet your new tutor</span></div><div class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(60px)\"><h1 class=\"text-[16vw] sm:text-[14vw] md:text-[12vw] lg:text-[10vw] xl:text-[9rem] leading-[0.82] tracking-tight text-foreground\" style=\"font-family:&#x27;Instrument Serif&#x27;, serif;font-style:italic\">that person.</h1><p class=\"font-mono text-base sm:text-lg md:text-xl text-muted-foreground uppercase tracking-[0.25em] mt-6\">for anything you want to learn.</p></div><div class=\"w-full max-w-xl mt-16 space-y-4 text-left\" style=\"opacity:0\"><div class=\"flex justify-end\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateX(40px)\"><div class=\"bg-foreground text-background px-5 py-3.5 max-w-[82%] border-2 border-foreground brutalist-shadow\"><p class=\"font-sans text-sm sm:text-base leading-snug\">wait, why does my function return undefined here? 😭</p></div></div><div class=\"flex justify-start\" style=\"opacity:0\"><div class=\"bg-background border-2 border-foreground px-4 py-3 brutalist-shadow flex items-center gap-2\"><div class=\"flex gap-1 items-end h-4\"><span class=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-primary animate-bounce\" style=\"animation-delay:0ms\"></span><span class=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-primary animate-bounce\" style=\"animation-delay:150ms\"></span><span class=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-primary animate-bounce\" style=\"animation-delay:300ms\"></span></div><span class=\"font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-muted-foreground\">Assign is thinking...</span></div></div><div class=\"flex justify-start\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateX(-40px)\"><div class=\"bg-background px-5 py-3.5 max-w-[82%] border-2 border-foreground brutalist-shadow-sm\"><p class=\"font-sans text-sm sm:text-base leading-snug text-foreground\">good catch — let&#x27;s trace through it together. what did you <em>expect</em> it to return on line 12?</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"w-full border-y-2 border-foreground bg-primary py-3.5 overflow-hidden flex-shrink-0\"><div class=\"flex animate-marquee whitespace-nowrap\" style=\"width:max-content\"><span class=\"flex items-center font-mono font-bold text-sm sm:text-base tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-foreground\"><span class=\"flex items-center\"><span class=\"mx-4\">LAW</span><