OLOGY</span><span class=\"opacity-60\">·</span></span><span class=\"flex items-center\"><span class=\"mx-4\">LITERATURE</span><span class=\"opacity-60\">·</span></span></span><span class=\"flex items-center font-mono font-bold text-sm sm:text-base tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-foreground\"><span class=\"flex items-center\"><span class=\"mx-4\">LAW</span><span class=\"opacity-60\">·</span></span><span class=\"flex items-center\"><span class=\"mx-4\">FINANCE</span><span class=\"opacity-60\">·</span></span><span class=\"flex items-center\"><span class=\"mx-4\">CODING</span><span class=\"opacity-60\">·</span></span><span class=\"flex items-center\"><span class=\"mx-4\">AI</span><span class=\"opacity-60\">·</span></span><span class=\"flex items-center\"><span class=\"mx-4\">MEDICINE</span><span class=\"opacity-60\">·</span></span><span class=\"flex items-center\"><span class=\"mx-4\">DESIGN</span><span class=\"opacity-60\">·</span></span><span class=\"flex items-center\"><span class=\"mx-4\">HISTORY</span><span class=\"opacity-60\">·</span></span><span class=\"flex items-center\"><span class=\"mx-4\">PHILOSOPHY</span><span class=\"opacity-60\">·</span></span><span class=\"flex items-center\"><span class=\"mx-4\">MATHS</span><span class=\"opacity-60\">·</span></span><span class=\"flex items-center\"><span class=\"mx-4\">ECONOMICS</span><span class=\"opacity-60\">·</span></span><span class=\"flex items-center\"><span class=\"mx-4\">BIOLOGY</span><span class=\"opacity-60\">·</span></span><span class=\"flex items-center\"><span class=\"mx-4\">LITERATURE</span><span class=\"opacity-60\">·</span></span></span></div></div></section><section class=\"bg-foreground text-background py-32 relative overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center pointer-events-none overflow-hidden select-none opacity-[0.04]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"text-background leading-none whitespace-nowrap font-sans font-black\" style=\"font-size:22vw;letter-spacing:-0.05em\">ASSIGN</span></div><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-24 mb-24\"><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateX(-60px)\"><h2 class=\"text-6xl md:text-8xl leading-[0.88]\" style=\"font-family:&#x27;Instrument Serif&#x27;, serif;font-style:italic\">Rich kids<br/>had tutors.</h2></div><div class=\"flex items-end lg:justify-end\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateX(60px)\"><p class=\"font-mono text-xl md:text-2xl text-background/60 uppercase tracking-widest max-w-md lg:text-right leading-relaxed\">Everyone else<br/>figured it out alone.</p></div></div><div class=\"text-center\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(60px)\"><span class=\"text-[15vw] leading-none tracking-tight\" style=\"font-family:&#x27;Instrument Serif&#x27;, serif;font-style:italic;color:hsl(208 82% 57%);display:block\">Not anymore.</span></div><div class=\"mt-24 pt-16 border-t-2 border-background/20 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(40px)\"><div><div class=\"font-mono text-7xl md:text-8xl font-bold tracking-tighter text-background\"><span>0</span></div><p class=\"font-sans text-lg text-background/50 uppercase tracking-widest mt-3\">Students worldwide</p></div><div><div class=\"font-mono text-7xl md:text-8xl font-bold tracking-tighter\" style=\"color:hsl(208 82% 57%)\">1</div><p class=\"font-sans text-lg text-background/50 uppercase tracking-widest mt-3\">Tutor you deserve. Assign.</p></div></div></div></section><section id=\"features\" class=\"py-32 bg-background relative z-10\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><div class=\"mb-20\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 mb-6\"><div class=\"h-px flex-1 bg-foreground/10\"></div><span class=\"font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-muted-foreground\">(02) What we do</span><div class=\"h-px flex-1 bg-foreground/10\"></div></div><div class=\"text-center\"><h2 class=\"text-5xl md:text-7xl lg:text-8xl leading-[0.9]\" style=\"font-family:&#x27;Instrument Serif&#x27;, serif;font-style:italic\">Four ways to learn.</h2><p class=\"font-mono text-base uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-muted-foreground mt-6\">Pick your weapon.</p></div></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 lg:gap-8\"><div class=\"group border-2 border-foreground brutalist-shadow-hover bg-card flex flex-col overflow-hidden\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(60px)\"><div class=\"p-7 flex-1\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-6\"><span class=\"font-mono text-3xl font-bold text-foreground/20\">01</span><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3\"><div class=\"w-3 h-3 bg-blue-500 border-2 border-foreground\"></div><span class=\"font-mono text-[11px] font-bold px-3 py-1 border-2 border-foreground bg-background brutalist-shadow-sm uppercase tracking-wider\">FOR BUILDERS</span></div></div><h3 class=\"font-sans font-bold text-2xl mb-4 leading-tight\">Code like you have a senior dev on speed dial.</h3><p class=\"font-sans text-muted-foreground text-base leading-relaxed\">Built codes with you, teaches as it goes, drops projects after each level. Every breakthrough unlocks XP. Gamified from day one.</p></div><div class=\"h-56 border-t-2 border-foreground bg-muted/40 overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"font-mono text-xs text-foreground p-5 bg-background h-full border-t-2 border-foreground flex flex-col gap-2.5\"><div class=\"flex justify-between items-center pb-3 border-b border-foreground/10 mb-1\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><div class=\"w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-red-400\"></div><div class=\"w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-yellow-400\"></div><div class=\"w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-green-400\"></div><span class=\"ml-2 text-muted-foreground\">main.ts</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><div class=\"bg-primary/20 text-primary px-2.5 py-1 text-[10px] font-bold tracking-widest uppercase\">LVL 4</div><div class=\"bg-yellow-400 text-foreground px-2 py-1 text-[10px] font-bold\">🔥 7</div></div></div><div class=\"space-y-1 leading-relaxed\"><p><span class=\"text-purple-500\">function</span> <span class=\"text-blue-500\">calculateXP</span><span class=\"text-foreground/60\">(base, streak) <!-- -->{</span></p><p class=\"pl-4 text-green-500 italic text-[10px]\">// Assign: nice — can you see why this grows exponentially?</p><p class=\"pl-4\"><span class=\"text-orange-500\">return</span> base * (1 + (streak * 0.1));</p><p class=\"text-foreground/60\">}</p></div><div class=\"mt-auto\"><div class=\"flex justify-between text-[10px] mb-1 text-muted-foreground uppercase tracking-widest\"><span>Progress</span><span>850 / 1000 XP</span></div><div class=\"h-2 border border-foreground/20 bg-muted\"><div class=\"h-full bg-primary\" style=\"width:85%\"></div></div></div></div></div><a class=\"flex items-center justify-between px-7 py-4 border-t-2 border-foreground bg-foreground text-background hover:bg-primary transition-colors duration-150\" href=\"/build\"><span class=\"font-mono text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest\">Try <!-- -->BUILDERS<!-- --> →</span><span class=\"font-mono text-[10px] text-background/50 uppercase tracking-widest\">Live preview</span></a></div><div class=\"group border-2 border-foreground brutalist-shadow-hover bg-card flex flex-col overflow-hidden\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(60px)\"><div class=\"p-7 flex-1\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-6\"><span class=\"font-mono text-3xl font-bold text-foreground/20\">02</span><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3\"><div class=\"w-3 h-3 bg-yellow-400 border-2 border-foreground\"></div><span class=\"font-mono text-[11px] font-bold px-3 py-1 border-2 border-foreground bg-background brutalist-shadow-sm uppercase tracking-wider\">FOR CURIOUS MINDS</span></div></div><h3 class=\"font-sans font-bold text-2xl mb-4 leading-tight\">One question. Properly understood.</h3><p class=\"font-sans text-muted-foreground text-base leading-relaxed\">Not another wall of text from GPT. Spark flips it — you explain it back. It spots the gaps, closes them. You leave actually knowing it.</p></div><div class=\"h-56 border-t-2 border-foreground bg-muted/40 overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"p-5 flex flex-col gap-3 h-full border-t-2 border-foreground bg-background justify-end\"><div class=\"self-end max-w-[80%] bg-foreground text-background p-3.5 border-2 border-foreground brutalist-shadow-sm\"><p class=\"text-sm leading-snug\">So inflation is just when money loses value?</p></div><div class=\"self-start max-w-[82%] bg-background border-2 border-foreground p-3.5 brutalist-shadow-sm\"><p class=\"text-sm leading-snug\">close! but tell me — what happens to <em>prices</em> when money loses value? 🤔</p></div><div class=\"self-end max-w-[80%] bg-foreground text-background p-3.5 border-2 border-foreground brutalist-shadow-sm\"><p class=\"text-sm leading-snug\">oh — they go up!</p></div><div class=\"self-start max-w-[82%] bg-background border-2 border-foreground p-3.5 brutalist-shadow-sm\"><p class=\"text-sm leading-snug\">exactly. so what is inflation really? say it back to me 👏</p></div></div></div><a class=\"flex items-center justify-between px-7 py-4 border-t-2 border-foreground bg-foreground text-background hover:bg-primary transition-colors duration-150\" href=\"/spark\"><span class=\"font-mono text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest\">Try <!-- -->MINDS<!-- --> →</span><span class=\"font-mono text-[10px] text-background/50 uppercase tracking-widest\">Live preview</span></a></div><div class=\"group border-2 border-foreground brutalist-shadow-hover bg-card flex flex-col overflow-hidden\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(60px)\"><div class=\"p-7 flex-1\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-6\"><span class=\"font-mono text-3xl font-bold text-foreground/20\">03</span><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3\"><div class=\"w-3 h-3 bg-green-400 border-2 border-foreground\"></div><span class=\"font-mono text-[11px] font-bold px-3 py-1 border-2 border-foreground bg-background brutalist-shadow-sm uppercase tracking-wider\">FOR LEARNERS</span></div></div><h3 class=\"font-sans font-bold text-2xl mb-4 leading-tight\">Your personal Coursera. But actually personal.</h3><p class=\"font-sans text-muted-foreground text-base leading-relaxed\">Tell Assign what you want to learn. It builds a roadmap based on what you already know. Teaching style stays the same: you explain it, it checks you.</p></div><div class=\"h-56 border-t-2 border-foreground bg-muted/40 overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"p-5 h-full border-t-2 border-foreground bg-background flex flex-col justify-center gap-3 relative\"><div class=\"absolute left-[2.35rem] top-8 bottom-8 w-0.5 bg-foreground/10\"></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 relative z-10\"><div class=\"w-4 h-4 border-2 border-foreground flex-shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center bg-green-400\"><span class=\"text-foreground text-[8px]\">✓</span></div><div class=\"flex-1 flex justify-between items-center py-2 px-3 border border-foreground/10 \"><span class=\"font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-wider \">Python Basics</span><span class=\"font-mono text-[10px] text-muted-foreground\">250 XP</span></div></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 relative z-10\"><div class=\"w-4 h-4 border-2 border-foreground flex-shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center bg-primary animate-pulse\"></div><div class=\"flex-1 flex justify-between items-center py-2 px-3 border border-foreground/10 bg-primary/10 border-primary\"><span class=\"font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-wider font-bold\">Data Structures</span><span class=\"font-mono text-[10px] text-muted-foreground\">180 XP</span></div></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 relative z-10\"><div class=\"w-4 h-4 border-2 border-foreground flex-shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center bg-muted\"></div><div class=\"flex-1 flex justify-between items-center py-2 px-3 border border-foreground/10 opacity-40\"><span class=\"font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-wider \">Algorithms</span><span class=\"font-mono text-[10px] text-muted-foreground\">300 XP</span></div></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 relative z-10\"><div class=\"w-4 h-4 border-2 border-foreground flex-shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center bg-muted\"></div><div class=\"flex-1 flex justify-between items-center py-2 px-3 border border-foreground/10 opacity-40\"><span class=\"font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-wider \">System Design</span><span class=\"font-mono text-[10px] text-muted-foreground\">500 XP</span></div></div></div></div><a class=\"flex items-center justify-between px-7 py-4 border-t-2 border-foreground bg-foreground text-background hover:bg-primary transition-colors duration-150\" href=\"/trek\"><span class=\"font-mono text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest\">Try <!-- -->LEARNERS<!-- --> →</span><span class=\"font-mono text-[10px] text-background/50 uppercase tracking-widest\">Live preview</span></a></div><div class=\"group border-2 border-foreground brutalist-shadow-hover bg-card flex flex-col overflow-hidden\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(60px)\"><div class=\"p-7 flex-1\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-6\"><span class=\"font-mono text-3xl font-bold text-foreground/20\">04</span><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3\"><div class=\"w-3 h-3 bg-red-400 border-2 border-foreground\"></div><span class=\"font-mono text-[11px] font-bold px-3 py-1 border-2 border-foreground bg-background brutalist-shadow-sm uppercase tracking-wider\">FOR EXAM WARRIORS</span></div></div><h3 class=\"font-sans font-bold text-2xl mb-4 leading-tight\">Prep smarter. Not harder.</h3><p class=\"font-sans text-muted-foreground text-base leading-relaxed\">Flashcards got a glow-up. AI-generated question banks, spaced repetition, mock exams. Recall pinpoints your weak spots and drills them until they stick.</p></div><div class=\"h-56 border-t-2 border-foreground bg-muted/40 overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"p-6 h-full border-t-2 border-foreground bg-background flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-4\"><div class=\"w-full max-h-[110px] relative\" style=\"transform-style:preserve-3d;perspective:800px\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-background border-2 border-foreground brutalist-shadow flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-4\" style=\"backface-visibility:hidden\"><span class=\"font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-muted-foreground mb-2\">Question</span><span class=\"font-serif text-xl text-center\">What is Mitosis?</span></div><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-foreground text-background border-2 border-foreground flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-4\" style=\"backface-visibility:hidden;transform:rotateY(180deg)\"><span class=\"font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-background/50 mb-2\">Answer</span><span class=\"font-sans text-sm text-center leading-snug\">Cell division producing two genetically identical daughter cells.</span></div></div><div class=\"flex gap-3 mt-2\"><div class=\"border-2 border-foreground px-4 py-2 font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-wider bg-red-100 text-red-700 brutalist-shadow-sm\">Again</div><div class=\"border-2 border-foreground px-4 py-2 font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-wider bg-yellow-100 text-yellow-700 brutalist-shadow-sm\">Hard</div><div class=\"border-2 border-foreground px-4 py-2 font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-wider bg-green-100 text-green-700 brutalist-shadow-sm\">Got it ✓</div></div></div></div><a class=\"flex items-center justify-between px-7 py-4 border-t-2 border-foreground bg-foreground text-background hover:bg-primary transition-colors duration-150\" href=\"/recall\"><span class=\"font-mono text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest\">Try <!-- -->WARRIORS<!-- --> →</span><span class=\"font-mono text-[10px] text-background/50 uppercase tracking-widest\">Live preview</span></a></div></div></div></section><section id=\"how-it-works\" class=\"py-32 bg-primary relative overflow-hidden border-y-2 border-foreground\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center pointer-events-none overflow-hidden select-none\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"font-serif italic leading-none whitespace-nowrap text-foreground\" style=\"font-size:28vw;opacity:0.06\">talk to it</span></div><div class=\"max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10\"><div class=\"text-center mb-14\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-center gap-4 mb-6\"><div class=\"h-px w-16 bg-foreground/30\"></div><span class=\"font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-foreground/60\">(03) How it works</span><div class=\"h-px w-16 bg-foreground/30\"></div></div><h2 class=\"text-5xl md:text-7xl text-foreground mb-4\" style=\"font-family:&#x27;Instrument Serif&#x27;, serif;font-style:italic\">Talk to it.<br/>Like a friend.</h2><p class=\"font-mono text-sm text-foreground/60 uppercase tracking-widest\">No robotic bullet points. Just back and forth until you get it.</p></div><div class=\"bg-background border-4 border-foreground brutalist-shadow-lg flex flex-col overflow-hidden\" style=\"min-height:480px\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 px-6 py-4 border-b-2 border-foreground bg-card\"><div class=\"flex gap-1.5\"><div class=\"w-3 h-3 bg-red-400 border border-red-600\"></div><div class=\"w-3 h-3 bg-yellow-400 border border-yellow-600\"></div><div class=\"w-3 h-3 bg-green-400 border border-green-600\"></div></div><div class=\"flex-1 text-center\"><span class=\"font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-muted-foreground\">Assign · Neural Networks</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-1.5\"><div class=\"w-2 h-2 bg-green-500 animate-pulse\"></div><span class=\"font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wider text-muted-foreground\">Live</span></div></div><div class=\"flex-1 p-6 space-y-5 overflow-y-auto\"></div><div class=\"border-t-2 border-foreground p-4 bg-card flex gap-3\"><div class=\"flex-1 bg-background border-2 border-foreground px-4 py-3 font-mono text-sm text-muted-foreground flex items-center\">Ask anything...</div><button class=\"bg-foreground text-background border-2 border-foreground px-6 py-3 font-mono text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-primary hover:border-primary transition-colors\">Send</button></div></div></div></section><section class=\"py-32 bg-background\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center\"><div><h2 class=\"font-serif italic text-6xl md:text-8xl mb-6\">Learning that actually sticks.</h2><p class=\"font-sans text-xl text-muted-foreground mb-8\">We ripped off the best parts of video games so you can&#x27;t put education down. XP, streaks, levels. It works.</p><ul class=\"space-y-6 font-mono text-lg uppercase tracking-wider\"><li class=\"flex items-center gap-4\"><div class=\"w-8 h-8 bg-green-400 border-2 border-foreground brutalist-shadow flex items-center justify-center text-foreground font-bold\">1</div>Earn XP for every concept explained</li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-4\"><div class=\"w-8 h-8 bg-yellow-400 border-2 border-foreground brutalist-shadow flex items-center justify-center text-foreground font-bold\">2</div>Maintain streaks to unlock perks</li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-4\"><div class=\"w-8 h-8 bg-blue-400 border-2 border-foreground brutalist-shadow flex items-center justify-center text-foreground font-bold\">3</div>Level up your expertise</li></ul></div><div class=\"relative\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-primary translate-x-4 translate-y-4 border-2 border-foreground pointer-events-none\"></div><div class=\"bg-card border-2 border-foreground p-8 relative z-10\"><div class=\"flex justify-between items-end mb-8 border-b-2 border-foreground/10 pb-6\"><div><p class=\"font-mono text-sm text-muted-foreground mb-1 uppercase\">Current Rank</p><h3 class=\"font-sans font-bold text-4xl\">Level 7 Coder</h3></div><div class=\"text-right\"><div class=\"text-5xl\">🔥</div><p class=\"font-mono font-bold mt-2\">12 DAY STREAK</p></div></div><div class=\"space-y-8\"><div><div class=\"flex justify-between font-mono text-sm font-bold mb-2\"><span>REACT BASICS</span><span>850 / 1000 XP</span></div><div class=\"h-6 w-full border-2 border-foreground bg-muted p-0.5\"><div class=\"h-full bg-blue-500\" style=\"width:0%\"></div></div></div><div><div class=\"flex justify-between font-mono text-sm font-bold mb-2\"><span>ALGORITHMS</span><span>420 / 500 XP</span></div><div class=\"h-6 w-full border-2 border-foreground bg-muted p-0.5\"><div class=\"h-full bg-green-400\" style=\"width:0%\"></div></div></div><div class=\"pt-6 mt-6 border-t-2 border-foreground/10 text-center\"><span class=\"inline-block bg-yellow-400 text-foreground border-2 border-foreground font-mono font-bold px-4 py-2 brutalist-shadow-sm rotate-[-2deg]\">⭐ NEW ACHIEVEMENT UNLOCKED: &quot;BUG SQUASHER&quot;</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section id=\"testimonials\" class=\"py-32 bg-muted border-t-2 border-foreground\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 mb-8\"><div class=\"h-px flex-1 bg-foreground/10\"></div><span class=\"font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-muted-foreground\">(04) Wall of love</span><div class=\"h-px flex-1 bg-foreground/10\"></div></div><div class=\"text-center mb-20\"><h2 class=\"text-5xl md:text-7xl lg:text-8xl leading-[0.9]\" style=\"font-family:&#x27;Instrument Serif&#x27;, serif;font-style:italic\">Don&#x27;t take our word for it.</h2></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6\"><div class=\"border-2 border-foreground bg-background flex flex-col brutalist-shadow-hover\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(50px)\"><div class=\"p-8 flex-1\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-8\"><div class=\"w-2.5 h-2.5 bg-blue-500 border border-foreground\"></div><span class=\"font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-muted-foreground\">via <!-- -->Built</span></div><div class=\"font-serif text-6xl text-foreground/10 leading-none mb-2 select-none\">&quot;</div><p class=\"font-sans text-lg leading-relaxed text-foreground\">Assign didn&#x27;t just give me the answers. It forced me to actually understand memory management in C. I passed the interview.</p></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 px-8 py-5 border-t-2 border-foreground bg-card mt-auto\"><div class=\"w-10 h-10 bg-foreground text-background font-mono font-bold flex items-center justify-center text-sm border-2 border-foreground brutalist-shadow-sm flex-shrink-0\">SJ</div><div><p class=\"font-sans font-semibold text-sm\">Sarah J.</p><p class=\"font-mono text-[10px] text-muted-foreground uppercase tracking-wider\">SWE Intern · Google</p></div></div></div><div class=\"border-2 border-foreground bg-background flex flex-col brutalist-shadow-hover\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(50px)\"><div class=\"p-8 flex-1\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-8\"><div class=\"w-2.5 h-2.5 bg-green-400 border border-foreground\"></div><span class=\"font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-muted-foreground\">via <!-- -->Trek</span></div><div class=\"font-serif text-6xl text-foreground/10 leading-none mb-2 select-none\">&quot;</div><p class=\"font-sans text-lg leading-relaxed text-foreground\">It&#x27;s like having a professor who never gets tired of your &#x27;stupid&#x27; questions. Trek mapped out my entire machine learning curriculum.</p></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 px-8 py-5 border-t-2 border-foreground bg-card mt-auto\"><div class=\"w-10 h-10 bg-foreground text-background font-mono font-bold flex items-center justify-center text-sm border-2 border-foreground brutalist-shadow-sm flex-shrink-0\">MT</div><div><p class=\"font-sans font-semibold text-sm\">Marcus T.</p><p class=\"font-mono text-[10px] text-muted-foreground uppercase tracking-wider\">CS Major · NYU</p></div></div></div><div class=\"border-2 border-foreground bg-background flex flex-col brutalist-shadow-hover\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(50px)\"><div class=\"p-8 flex-1\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-8\"><div class=\"w-2.5 h-2.5 bg-red-400 border border-foreground\"></div><span class=\"font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-muted-foreground\">via <!-- -->Recall</span></div><div class=\"font-serif text-6xl text-foreground/10 leading-none mb-2 select-none\">&quot;</div><p class=\"font-sans text-lg leading-relaxed text-foreground\">I used Recall to prep for my bar exam. The way it identified my weak spots in contract law was honestly terrifying. But brilliant.</p></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 px-8 py-5 border-t-2 border-foreground bg-card mt-auto\"><div class=\"w-10 h-10 bg-foreground text-background font-mono font-bold flex items-center justify-center text-sm border-2 border-foreground brutalist-shadow-sm flex-shrink-0\">ER</div><div><p class=\"font-sans font-semibold text-sm\">Elena R.</p><p class=\"font-mono text-[10px] text-muted-foreground uppercase tracking-wider\">Law Student · Columbia</p></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"bg-foreground py-32 border-t-2 border-foreground relative overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none opacity-[0.05]\" style=\"background-image:linear-gradient(to right, #f1f0ee 1px, transparent 1px), linear-gradient(to bottom, #f1f0ee 1px, transparent 1px);background-size:3rem 3rem\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center relative z-10\"><div style=\"opacity:0\"><p class=\"font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-background/40 mb-6\">Early Access</p><h2 class=\"leading-[0.85] text-background mb-10\" style=\"font-family:&#x27;Instrument Serif&#x27;, serif;font-style:italic;font-size:clamp(3.5rem, 12vw, 11rem)\">Your tutor<br/>is waiting.</h2><p class=\"font-mono text-lg text-background/50 uppercase tracking-widest mb-16\">Join the waitlist. Be first. Learn different.</p></div><form class=\"max-w-lg mx-auto flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-0 border-2 border-background brutalist-shadow-white-lg\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><input id=\"waitlist\" type=\"email\" placeholder=\"your@email.com\" required=\"\" class=\"flex-1 bg-foreground text-background border-0 border-r-2 border-background px-6 py-4 font-mono text-sm placeholder:text-background/30 focus:outline-none focus:bg-background/5\" value=\"\"/><button type=\"submit\" class=\"bg-background text-foreground px-8 py-4 font-mono font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-primary hover:text-foreground transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">Get Access →</button></form><p class=\"font-mono text-xs text-background/30 mt-8 uppercase tracking-widest\">No credit card. No BS. Just learning.</p><div class=\"flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4 mt-16 pt-12 border-t border-background/10\"><div class=\"font-mono text-xs text-background/40 uppercase tracking-widest border border-background/10 px-4 py-2\">Built · for coders</div><div class=\"font-mono text-xs text-background/40 uppercase tracking-widest border border-background/10 px-4 py-2\">Spark · for questions</div><div class=\"font-mono text-xs text-background/40 uppercase tracking-widest border border-background/10 px-4 py-2\">Trek · for learners</div><div class=\"font-mono text-xs text-background/40 uppercase tracking-widest border border-background/10 px-4 py-2\">Recall · for exams</div></div></div></section><footer class=\"bg-foreground text-background py-8 border-t border-background/20\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-4\"><div class=\"font-mono font-bold tracking-tight text-xl flex items-center gap-2\"><svg width=\"20\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 30\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M12.8492 24.4945H24V29.962C21.4073 29.8743 18.7213 30.0785 16.1397 29.9643C13.2258 29.836 10.5209 28.